    • put

      public void put(String url, LicenseDownloader.LicenseDownloadResult entry)
      Binds the given url to the give LicenseDownloader.LicenseDownloadResult. If both enforcingUniqueSha1s and LicenseDownloader.LicenseDownloadResult.isSuccess() are true and an entry with the given LicenseDownloader.LicenseDownloadResult.getSha1() already exists in sha1ToFile, asserts that both the added and the available entry point at the same file.
      Parameters:
      url - the URL the given entry comes from
      entry - the result of downloading from url
